FN: Mere
SL: The science behind “menopause belly”, bloating, and low energy
PH: And the “flat belly detox” that works for me…
Did you overdo it at Thanksgiving?
If so, you might be tempted to diet and “start fresh”.
But I’m sorry, that won’t work.
You see, every diet under the sun focuses on calories…
And that’s why none of them work.
Instead I want to share something personal for you to try today — the kind of thing I wish someone had told me when I was deep in it.
After I had my two kiddos, Sage and Cruz, I felt like a stranger in my own body.
The athlete in me? She was exhausted.
The go-getter? Burnt out.
And honestly… the woman looking back at me in the mirror felt like someone I didn’t even recognize anymore.
I had battled postpartum depression, my hormones were a mess, and no matter how “healthy” I ate or how hard I worked out… the scale wouldn’t budge.
I was bloated, frustrated, and constantly wondering: “What is wrong with me?”
Turns out, it wasn’t willpower.
It wasn’t the workouts.
It was my metabolism and hormones, they’d shifted after 40, and I needed to shift with them.
That’s when I started experimenting with what I now call my fat-boosting morning smoothie and everything started to change.
It’s simple. It’s delicious. And it’s the reason I finally started to feel like me again.
It helps flip your body’s “MetaSwitch” back ON: so fat starts burning instead of storing.
It reduces bloating and supports smoother digestion.
It helps calm stress hormones that can block weight loss.
And it gives your metabolism the nudge it needs: no crash diets, no stimulants.
This one daily habit helped me drop stubborn weight, stop feeling so inflamed, and feel energized again, without cutting carbs or counting every bite.
And now?
I never start my morning without it. I just mix a scoop of my special formula into water, almond milk, or a smoothie and sip it while the dogs (Ghost and Loka) run circles around the kitchen and Cruz begs for pancakes.
It’s easy. It tastes good. And it works.
Once I started giving my body the support it’s been craving. And the difference speaks for itself.
I call it my fat-burning smoothie.
But it’s really so much more than that.
It’s a ritual that supports your body at the root: gut, hormones, metabolism all in one.
And I’d love for you to try it.
Click here to make your first fat-burning smoothie.
You don’t need to do it all. Just take one smart step today.
With love,
Mere
P.S. This is your fat-boosting smoothie in a scoop. Packed with 50+ superfoods, adaptogens, and gut-loving ingredients… and it actually tastes good. Try it now, completely risk-free with my 60 day money back guarantee. Get it here.
